        VehicleRoutingAlgorithm algo = Jsprit.createAlgorithm(vrp);
        return Solutions.bestOf(algo.searchSolutions());
    });
}
```

Alternatively, use the built-in `THREADS` parameter to parallelise *insertion evaluation*
within a single solve (thread-safe internally):
```java
Jsprit.Builder.newInstance(vrp).setProperty(Jsprit.Parameter.THREADS, "4").buildAlgorithm();
```

